<subSubSection pageId="106" pageNumber="107" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="106" pageNumber="107">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="106" pageNumber="107">A remarkable species with flowers clustered at the apex of a very long peduncle. The stigmas are short and stout and commonly 3 in number.</paragraph>
